               <INFO_ADD>
                  <P>The University applied to the National Institute of Health Research for the establishment of an NIHR Global Health Research Unit, which has been subsequently awarded. The Unit is in the process of seeking additional funds for future trials in the partner countries. Contracts are being agreed and signed with the Hubs in the respective areas with a view to increase the roll out in the future.</P>
